Please listen to this urgent and time-sensitive message with a specific call-to-action!  Make sure to take this action every time the clock hit's 11:00 am and 11:00 pm in your own time zone, for the next 48 hours, for a total of 4 times in the next 48 hours.  Set an alarm on your phone.  Write a note and put it on the fridge.  What ever it takes, remember to do this.  It's only going to be effective if EVERYONE puts their mind to the task.  And please, share this with ALL your friends, family and loved ones.  Ask them to do the same thing, and ask them to pass this on and pay it forward.  With gratitude and blessings!
